0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:01:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生日買部Gameboy比我，個時岩岩出幾百蚊部好撚貴。人工重係得幾千蚊既年代。部機依家重留左係到，雖然已經玩唔到，多謝你呀媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細細個最深刻都係同兩老出街買gameboy俾我<br />\n都應該唔止廿年<br />\n因為當時路過見到人地玩我又來想要<br />\n不過成千蚊<br />\n扭下計就買左俾我<br />\n到而家都仲記得係因為我大多幾年之後先知道<br />\n當時嘅一千蚊已經係好多錢<br />\n屋企環境唔算太好<br />\n但係有d咩要求都盡量滿足我<br />\n所以而家到我孝順返你地喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187adbffac85fa749930b3348fb622415923a5e3","tid":194230,"uid":34160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:03:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個用滕條打我背脊打到斷埋<br />\n用手肘撞落我條頸到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打點解覺得warm呀 你係咪m黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你真係好天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa00705481d3db9f7fa262e6f9c50480f204789","tid":194230,"uid":81828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:07:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>細個用滕條打我背脊打到斷埋<br />\n用手肘撞落我條頸到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打點解覺得warm呀 你係咪m黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你真係好天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1266e70cb0f8b9e001525fdd085d0c3b768a3f8","tid":194230,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:07:30.000Z","msg":"結婚前驚我無錢，問駛唔駛幫手，但男人老狗唔想結婚都要媽咪幫手比錢。<br />\n最終結婚前兩個月送左層市區八百呎半新樓，結婚當日再比左超過三十萬既金器比我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"38ab16c6f5c18325d8a66219d71bf4a0b188f5